                    <li>‚Ä¢ Lane departure warnings keep cars on track</li>
                  </ul>
                  <div class="bg-white p-3 rounded border">
                    <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-blue-800 mb-1">Result:</p>
                    <p class="text-xs text-blue-600">Road fatalities reduced by 50% since 1990s with safety tech</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="bg-red-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-red-200">
                  <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-red-800 mb-3">üè• Medical Safety</h3>
                  <p class="text-red-700 mb-3"><strong>Protecting Patients</strong></p>
                  <ul class="text-sm text-red-700 space-y-1 mb-3">
                    <li>‚Ä¢ IV pumps prevent medication overdoses</li>
                    <li>‚Ä¢ Heart monitors alert staff to emergencies</li>
                    <li>‚Ä¢ Surgical robots provide precision and steadiness</li>
                    <li>‚Ä¢ Automated dispensers reduce medication errors</li>
                  </ul>
                  <div class="bg-white p-3 rounded border">
                    <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-red-800 mb-1">Result:</p>
                    <p class="text-xs text-red-600">Medical errors reduced by 60% in automated systems</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="bg-yellow-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-yellow-200">
