                    <li>‚Ä¢ Autopilot systems maintain stable flight</li>
                    <li>‚Ä¢ Weather radar detects dangerous storms</li>
                    <li>‚Ä¢ Collision avoidance prevents mid-air crashes</li>
                    <li>‚Ä¢ Emergency landing systems activate automatically</li>
                  </ul>
                  <div class="bg-white p-3 rounded border">
                    <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-yellow-800 mb-1">Result:</p>
                    <p class="text-xs text-yellow-600">Commercial aviation is now 50x safer than in 1960s</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Everyday Safety Examples -->
            <div class="mb-8">
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Safety in Everyday Life</h2>
              
              <FlipCard frontTitle="Home Safety Systems" id="home-safety">
                <div slot="front">
                  <p><strong>Question:</strong> How do mechatronic systems keep your home safe?</p>
                  <p>Think about all the automated safety features around your house.</p>
                  <p><strong>Click to explore hidden safety systems ‚Üí</strong></p>
                </div>
                <div slot="back">
