                  <ul class="text-sm space-y-1 mb-3">
                    <li><strong>üî• Smoke detectors:</strong> Sensors detect smoke, sound alarm automatically</li>
                    <li><strong>üö® Security alarms:</strong> Motion sensors trigger alerts and camera recording</li>
                    <li><strong>üí® Carbon monoxide detectors:</strong> Detect deadly gas, alert occupants</li>
                    <li><strong>üöø GFCI outlets:</strong> Cut power instantly if electrical shock risk detected</li>
