                    <ul class="text-sm text-blue-700 space-y-1">
                      <li>‚Ä¢ Instantly alert multiple people and systems</li>
                      <li>‚Ä¢ Record everything for investigation</li>
                      <li>‚Ä¢ Coordinate responses across large areas</li>
                    </ul>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Future Safety Trends -->
            <div class="mb-8">
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Future of Mechatronic Safety</h2>
              
              <div class="space-y-4">
